    \trigorgon.onFirstComponent ] @fthochraeTop \karasParacletike'lookup
    markConditionalLigatureWideFthochraPsifiston;
  pos @baseLigsKentimataCombos [@gorga @digorga \trigorgon
    @gorga.onFirstComponent @digorga.onFirstComponent
    \trigorgon.onFirstComponent ] \karasParacletike'lookup
    markConditionalLigatureWideFthochraPsifiston;
  pos @baseLigsKentimataCombos [@gorga.onFirstComponent @digorga.onFirstComponent \trigorgon.onFirstComponent ]
    @fthochraeTop'lookup markConditionalLigatureWideFthochraPsifiston;
  pos @baseLigsKentimataCombos @fthochraeTop'lookup markConditionalLigatureWideFthochraPsifiston [@gorga.onFirstComponent @digorga.onFirstComponent \trigorgon.onFirstComponent ];
